  Version bump.

  17 Mar 2007; Petteri Räty <betelgeuse@gentoo.org>
  jgroups-2.2.7-r2.ebuild:
  Switch to java-pkg_dojavadoc, add the source use flag and disable unit tests
  because a lot of them fail.

  25 Oct 2006; Joshua Nichols <nichoj@gentoo.org> jgroups-2.2.7-r2.ebuild:
  Fixed failure with USE=doc, bug #152281. Cleanups for how it was migrated.

  14 Sep 2006; Joshua Nichols <nichoj@gentoo.org> jgroups-2.2.7-r1.ebuild:
  Removed unnecessary pkg_setup.

